These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-5-1::.
House: cape-cod, art-deco
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, pop
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, doctor
1. the doctor is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5
2. the fan of pop is the doctor##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| House          | art-deco    | cape-cod |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | skydiving |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | pop    |
| Job   | designer  | doctor |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-5-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, filmmaking
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, volleyball
2 different pets are kept: cat, rabbit
2 different games are played: billiard, bridge
1. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Hobby          | writing | filmmaking   |
| Sport   | volleyball        | baseball     |
| Pet           | cat         | rabbit     |
| Game     | billiard         | bridge |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-5-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, blend
There are 2 different nationalities: british, nigerian
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, trance
City: prague, london
1. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the right of the blend-smoker##5
2. the british is somewhere to the left of the fan of house##5
3. the nigerian is the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Cigar         | blend      | ritmeester    |
| Nationality           | british | nigerian |
| Music-Genre   | trance       | house    |
| City     | prague    | london     |

 #################################

 
