1. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person eating broccoli##5
2. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the mexican##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Beverage      | coffee  | 7up        |
| House         | gothic-revival | cape-cod |
